Furthermore, the personalization of UCAIR is provided on the client side.
UCAIR makes direct use of a user"s query history to benefit the same user immediately in the same search session.
(3) We propose a retrieval framework to integrate implicit user modeling with the interactive retrieval  process, while the previous work either studies implicit user modeling separately from retrieval [3] or only studies specific retrieval  models for exploiting implicit feedback to better match a query with documents [23, 27, 22].
